title: C64 Orchestra - Run 10 (2007) (FLAC)
description:
RUN 10 by C64 Orchestra, a chamber orchestra performing tunes from Commodore 64 games, with a bonus disc of the original tunes and more.

The tunes are composed by Rob Hubbard and Jeroen Tel. Scoring for C64 Orchestra was done by Rob Hubbard. C64 Orchestra are conductor Bas Wiegers and the Ricciotti Ensemble.

Copied with Exact Audio Copy V0.99 prebeta 4 in secure mode. Losslessly compressed with FLAC 1.2.1.
